</div><p class="lp-result-teaser__metric"><span class="counter" data-target="530000">0</span><span>+</span></p><p class="lp-result-teaser__text">people &amp; SMEs reached</p></div></article></div><a class="lp-result-teaser-group__link" href="/en/what-we-do/impact" aria-label="Link to a page"></a></section><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--two-column variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''18a44370-b3d8-4c8d-a12c-82754600d33d'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''47e3ecdea5c40aff4afc42d22ca97f1c6146a545'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1351''}" style="padding-bottom: 56.291666666667%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><h2>Our Work</h2><p>Through education, innovation, and entrepreneurship, we promote sustainable jobs, fair incomes, and functioning local markets. We apply a partnership-based, market-oriented, and effective approach.</p></div></div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do" class="variable-teaser__link"></a></article></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__fullsize" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="2d5687ea-67b5-4cf0-b0f6-c63b39f51f41"><div class="teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''8fe9c158-6f6c-4c4e-9545-e9868f545495'',''name'':''DSC00021.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''4d6534126eb1071beeeb42509d99c966045a8b5f'',''maxwidth'':''5421'',''originalwidth'':''5421'',''originalheight'':''2684''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.511160302527%"></div></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="container"><div class="teaser__box--wrapper col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 col-xl-5 offset-xl-0 col-xxl-4"><div class="teaser__box--content"><div class="teaser__box--title">Annual Report 2025</div><div class="teaser__box--text">In 2025, international development cooperation progressed against a backdrop of rising geopolitical uncertainty and continued demands for measurable impact. Swisscontact responded by focusing on relevant, future-oriented projects that delivered lasting impact. Our skills projects helped people acquire practical skills, resulting in new jobs and income-generating activities. The strengthening of local vocational education systems was a priority as well. At the same time, entrepreneurs and small businesses gained better access to markets, services, and finance. This strengthened their resilience and unlocked revenue growth. Together, these efforts reinforced local economies and showed how well‑designed development cooperation efforts continue to create value for partner countries and Switzerland alike.</div></div><div class="teaser__box--link"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports/annual-report-2025" class="teaser--link" title="Learn more"><span class="teaser--link-text">Learn more</span></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container resultTeaserGroup threeColumn"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><a class="stretched-link" href="/en/get-involved-with-us/corporate-partnerships"></a><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Corporate<br>partnerships</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Together with companies, we develop partnerships that combine economic activity with sustainable development. We support your own initiatives, explore possibilities within existing projects, or help plan a feasibility study. Always with your individual corporate goals in mind.</p></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser__link-text">All offers for companies</div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><a class="stretched-link" href="/en/get-involved-with-us/philanthropic-engagement"></a><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Philanthropic<br>Engagement</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Philanthropic supporters such as foundations make vital contributions, whether through focused funding of specific topics or by introducing their own project ideas. These partnerships create tangible impact for people on the ground, based on shared values and goals.</p></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser__link-text">All philanthropic offers</div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><a class="stretched-link" href="/en/get-involved-with-us/support-swisscontact"></a><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Institutional<br>support</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Support our work and help improve living conditions for people in developing countries through individually tailored projects and partnerships.</p></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser__link-text">Support us</div></div></div></div><section class="container cta-teaser cta-teaser--2column"><div class="cta-teaser__content"><div class="cta-teaser__content--left"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content--image-wrap"><div class="image--size image--fullsize"><div class="content--image w-"><figure><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''24a81912-87e7-40d6-919f-61e86584e61c'',''name'':''RWA_PROMOST_Swisscontact_Content_Gathering_for_TVETs___-_RV8_3274_%281%29.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''74326503c424cd66f972f6a3beb951d10f45be24'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1600''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"></div></figure></div></div></div></div></div><div class="cta-teaser__content--right"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><h2>Would you like to get involved and support our work?</h2></div></div></div></div><div class="cta-teaser__cta"><div class="cta-banner"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="cta-banner__content col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8 offset-md-1 offset-lg-2"><p class="cta-banner__text">Find the right opportunity.</p><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us" class="cta-banner__link"><span class="cta-banner__link-text">Find the right opportunity.</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h2>News</h2></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/news" title="All news">All news</a></div><div class="teaserproxy__3col col-12 col-md-4" data-internezzo-teaser--groupedproxy data-internezzo-teaser--proxyajaxuri="/en?ajaxDestination%5Bidentifier%5D=teaserProxyResolver&amp;ajaxDestination%5BteaserNodeIdentifier%5D=ed7bc948-c920-40e9-bde5-b7c2b7d27e27&amp;ajaxDestination%5Bindex%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5BisLatest%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5Blanguage%5D="><div class="loader"><div class="loader__icon icon--top"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--center"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--bottom"></div></div></div><div class="teaserproxy__3col col-12 col-md-4" data-internezzo-teaser--groupedproxy data-internezzo-teaser--proxyajaxuri="/en?ajaxDestination%5Bidentifier%5D=teaserProxyResolver&amp;ajaxDestination%5BteaserNodeIdentifier%5D=ed7bc948-c920-40e9-bde5-b7c2b7d27e27&amp;ajaxDestination%5Bindex%5D=1&amp;ajaxDestination%5BisLatest%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5Blanguage%5D="><div class="loader"><div class="loader__icon icon--top"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--center"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--bottom"></div></div></div><div class="teaserproxy__3col col-12 col-md-4" data-internezzo-teaser--groupedproxy data-internezzo-teaser--proxyajaxuri="/en?ajaxDestination%5Bidentifier%5D=teaserProxyResolver&amp;ajaxDestination%5BteaserNodeIdentifier%5D=ed7bc948-c920-40e9-bde5-b7c2b7d27e27&amp;ajaxDestination%5Bindex%5D=2&amp;ajaxDestination%5BisLatest%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5Blanguage%5D="><div class="loader"><div class="loader__icon icon--top"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--center"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--bottom"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''4833331e-f8ce-4529-baf9-fe110b46f16c'',''name'':''preparando_el_terreno_para_siembra.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''640fddd4a5719264d6a6ba33791eda84a72b6f39'',''maxwidth'':''4800'',''originalwidth'':''4800'',''originalheight'':''2399''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.979166666667%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">For a sustainable and equitable future</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">Based in Zurich, Swisscontact is the independent, business-oriented foundation for international development cooperation. Founded in 1959 by leading Swiss companies, Swisscontact has promoted skills development and entrepreneurship to make a sustainable contribution to economic growth in developing and emerging countries.</p><a href="/en/about-us" class="variable-teaser__link"></a></div></article></div><div class="container"></div><div class="container"></div><div class="container"></div></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http:\/\/schema.org","@type":"NGO","@id":"\/en#ngo","name":"Swisscontact"}</script></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li