('/en/what-we-do', 'en', 'What we do - Site', 'Communities around the world are under pressure. Climate change is straining both rural communities and cities, outdated education systems are falling short, while economic inequality limits access to professional opportunities for many. At the same time, innovative businesses lack capital and reliable enabling environments. Our development work tackles these global challenges with practical solutions that empower people and strengthen systems – without burdening the environment.', '<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en" dir="ltr">
