"{''id'':''6159ff88-c18f-482f-8d27-9193ae08a971'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''531094119d262dbc60017c71d819ca76d8665e75'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li><li class="mainNav__item level1"><a href="/en/news"><span class="mainNav__text">News</span></a></li><li data-nezzo-mainnav-haschilds class="mainNav__item level1 sub"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a><div class="mainNav__level2--wrapper"><div class="mainNav__level2--content"><div><div class="mainNav__item--parent level2"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a></div><ul class="mainNav__level2" data-nezzo-mainnav-level="2"><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/mission-and-guiding-principles"><span class="mainNav__text">Mission and guiding principles</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><span class="mainNav__text">Sustainability strategy</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/code-of-conduct"><span class="mainNav__text">Code of conduct</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/foundation"><span class="mainNav__text">Foundation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/team"><span class="mainNav__text">Team</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''e783a2df-031c-4b4f-9d6b-0b9000d337ca'',''name'':''Monkshood_Krishi_Farm_Sahaj-3.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''c70a1d7d18ab438ac6dc75f1dbe143120ec0656e'',''maxwidth'':''9504'',''originalwidth'':''9504'',''originalheight'':''4707''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.526515151515%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">What we do</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Our work for a future full of opportunities</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">Communities around the world are under pressure. Climate change is straining both rural communities and cities, outdated education systems are falling short, while economic inequality limits access to professional opportunities for many. At the same time, innovative businesses lack capital and reliable enabling environments. Our development work tackles these global challenges with practical solutions that empower people and strengthen systems – without burdening the environment.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>Our Response to Global Challenges</h2><p>To achieve sustainable change, we focus on three core areas.</p></div></div></div><div class="container container content__advancedTextWithImage"><div class="advancedTextWithImage__inner"><div class="advancedTextWithImage__content yellow textColor--grey" style="background-color: #ffffff"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><h3>Skills and employment</h3><p>Though the world of work is undergoing rapid change, global education systems are not keeping pace. Millions of people, especially women and marginalised groups, lack access to relevant skills and training; systemic barriers prevent them from seizing new opportunities, threatening income security and the chance for a self-determined life.</p><p>Our solution for skills and employment:</p></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/initial-vocational-education-and-training">Initial vocational education &amp; training</a></p></div></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/labour-market-insertion">Labour market insertion</a></p></div></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/reskilling-and-upskilling">Reskilling &amp; upskilling</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class="advancedTextWithImage__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-respectheight="true" data-ari-params="{''id'':''29433843-b02c-4952-8afb-a45dac3d0fe7'',''name'':''Tilers_3.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''cb3e031fd5fc61e0dfd4a2efffcd3a6b67391231'',''maxwidth'':''3117'',''originalwidth'':''3117'',''originalheight'':''2078''}"></div></div></div></div><div class="container container content__advancedTextWithImage"><div class="advancedTextWithImage__inner"><div class="advancedTextWithImage__content yellow textColor--grey" style="background-color: #ffffff"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><h3>Enterprise development</h3><p>Many developing and emerging countries hold tremendous entrepreneurial potential. Yet funding gaps, fragile ecosystems, and limited market access hinder innovation. Better conditions are needed for businesses to grow, become more resilient, and create jobs.</p><p>How we support enterprise development:</p></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/growth-entrepreneurship">Growth entrepreneurship</a></p></div></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/sustainable-tourism">Sustainable tourism</a></p></div></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/trade">Trade</a></p></div></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/financial-inclusion">Financial inclusion</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class="advancedTextWithImage__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-respectheight="true" data-ari-params="{''id'':''b5e658eb-281f-4ac4-92b9-81280f6236a3'',''name'':''Website-Training-Webinar-Headerimage.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''235bbb6e67bf38cd8de8c54497dbe5c58894d96b'',''maxwidth'':''5584'',''originalwidth'':''5584'',''originalheight'':''3723''}"></div></div></div></div><div class="container container content__advancedTextWithImage"><div class="advancedTextWithImage__inner"><div class="advancedTextWithImage__content yellow textColor--grey" style="background-color: #ffffff"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><h3>Green transition</h3><p>Climate change and environmental degradation affect both rural and urban areas. Smallholder farmers struggle with soil degradation and unpredictable weather, while growing cities face overwhelmed infrastructure. This puts ecosystems and livelihoods increasingly out of balance.</p><p>How we drive green transformation:</p></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/sustainable-agriculture">Sustainable agriculture</a></p></div></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/green-cities">Green cities</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class="advancedTextWithImage__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-respectheight="true" data-ari-params="{''id'':''06b3852a-5e5b-4518-b4d8-aa40931105d9'',''name'':''NER_PEMJI_IMG_9719_%281%29.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''70067e16565ba94a85e8103da8742acd23da08d4'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1347''}"></div></div></div></div><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>Global projects</h2><p>We rely on sustainable, market-oriented development approaches that improve the quality of life for people in developing and emerging economies. The focus is on strengthening individual skills and business competitiveness.</p></div></div></div><div class="container content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="/en/projects">View all projects</a></p></div></div><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''4786f79d-a8b7-4dc4-8016-c465af7b21ea'',''name'':''Swisscontact_Lebanon_Short_Internship-By_Mazen_Yammine_62-1000x667.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''7d95a5daf8ff25a79c4c99c7919ab0ec58671acd'',''maxwidth'':''1000'',''originalwidth'':''1000'',''originalheight'':''500''}" style="padding-bottom: 50%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">Want to get involved and support us?</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">Find the right opportunity.</p><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us" class="variable-teaser__link"></a></div></article></div></div></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/imprint"><span class="item__footer--text">Imprint</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/privacy-statement"><span class="item__footer--text">Privacy statement</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/legal-notice"><span class="item__footer--text">Legal notice</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="javascript: UC_UI.showSecondLayer();"><span class="item__footer--text">Cookie settings</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="footer__content footer__centerContent col-lg-4"><div class="neos-contentcollection">
