/support-swisscontact"><span class="mainNav__text">Support Swisscontact</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6159ff88-c18f-482f-8d27-9193ae08a971'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''531094119d262dbc60017c71d819ca76d8665e75'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li><li class="mainNav__item level1"><a href="/en/news"><span class="mainNav__text">News</span></a></li><li data-nezzo-mainnav-haschilds class="mainNav__item level1 sub"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a><div class="mainNav__level2--wrapper"><div class="mainNav__level2--content"><div><div class="mainNav__item--parent level2"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a></div><ul class="mainNav__level2" data-nezzo-mainnav-level="2"><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/mission-and-guiding-principles"><span class="mainNav__text">Mission and guiding principles</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><span class="mainNav__text">Sustainability strategy</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/code-of-conduct"><span class="mainNav__text">Code of conduct</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/foundation"><span class="mainNav__text">Foundation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/team"><span class="mainNav__text">Team</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6159ff88-c18f-482f-8d27-9193ae08a971'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''531094119d262dbc60017c71d819ca76d8665e75'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Get involved with us</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Your commitment to sustainable development</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">We support you as a strong development partner: whether you are a company seeking to engage in social responsibility or a philanthropist looking for the right project. Swisscontact connects diverse actors and implements market-oriented development solutions together with private and public partners. Your commitment empowers people worldwide.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>Impactful opportunities – individually designed</h2><p>Effective development work succeeds when different perspectives and competencies come together. That’s why we seek partners who join us in tackling concrete challenges – whether with a thematic focus or a specific practical issue. Where sensible, we also promote public-private partnerships to further strengthen our offerings.</p></div></div></div><div class="container resultTeaserGroup threeColumn"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><a class="stretched-link" href="/en/get-involved-with-us/corporate-partnerships"></a><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Corporate<br>partnerships</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Together with companies, we develop partnerships that combine economic activity with sustainable development. We support your own initiatives, explore possibilities within existing projects, or help plan a feasibility study. Always with your individual corporate goals in mind.</p></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser__link-text">All offers for companies</div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><a class="stretched-link" href="/en/get-involved-with-us/philanthropic-engagement"></a><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Philanthropic<br>partnerships</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Philanthropic supporters such as foundations make vital contributions, whether through focused funding of specific topics or by introducing their own project ideas. These partnerships create tangible impact for people on the ground, based on shared values and goals.</p></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser__link-text">All philanthropic offers</div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><a class="stretched-link" href="/en/get-involved-with-us/support-swisscontact"></a><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Institutional<br>support</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Support our work and help improve living conditions for people in developing countries through individually tailored projects and partnerships.</p></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser__link-text">Support us</div></div></div></div><div class="container content__textwithimage"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="textwithimage--image col-md-5 col-lg-4 order-1"><div class="content--image w-"><figure><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''e0bf06bc-21d1-4f8f-9826-c6a5974ea88c'',''name'':''Omar_Kassa_bw_web.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''80f5eca82d42319deeba4e0b0d3a1fe7fea86c72'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></figure></div></div><div class="textwithimage--content col-md-5 col-lg-4 order-1"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Let’s find the right way for you to get involved – we are happy to advise you.</p><p><strong>Omar Kassab</strong><br>+41 44 454 17 90<br><a href="javascript:linkTo_UnCryptMailto(''vthy5rhzzhiGzdpzzjvuahja5vyn'',-7)"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="ff90929e8dd1949e8c8c9e9dbf8c88968c8c9c90918b9e9c8bd1908d98">[email&#160;protected]</span></a></p></div><div class="content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="javascript:linkTo_UnCryptMailto(''caof,yoggopNgkwggqcbhoqh,cfu'',-14)">Contact Us</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/imprint"><span class="item__footer--text">Imprint</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/privacy-statement"><span class="item__footer--text">Privacy statement</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/legal-notice"><span class="item__footer--text">Legal notice</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="javascript: UC_UI.showSecondLayer();"><span class="item__footer--text">Cookie settings</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="footer__content footer__centerContent col-lg-4"><div class="neos-contentcollection">
         <div class="content__text">
           <h3>Support Our Work</h3>
           <p>If you wish to make a donation or support our projects, please contact us directly using our inquiry form.</p>
           <p><a href="/en/footer/contact" style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Donation Inquiry Form</a></p>
         </div>
