ght'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li><li class="mainNav__item level1"><a href="/en/news"><span class="mainNav__text">News</span></a></li><li data-nezzo-mainnav-haschilds class="mainNav__item level1 sub  current"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a><div class="mainNav__level2--wrapper"><div class="mainNav__level2--content"><div><div class="mainNav__item--parent level2"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a></div><ul class="mainNav__level2" data-nezzo-mainnav-level="2"><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/mission-and-guiding-principles"><span class="mainNav__text">Mission and guiding principles</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><span class="mainNav__text">Sustainability strategy</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/code-of-conduct"><span class="mainNav__text">Code of conduct</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/foundation"><span class="mainNav__text">Foundation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/team"><span class="mainNav__text">Team</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">About us</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>For a sustainable and equitable future</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">Headquartered in Zurich, Swisscontact is the independent, business-oriented foundation for international development cooperation. Founded in 1959 by leading Swiss companies, Swisscontact has promoted skills development and entrepreneurship to make a sustainable contribution to economic growth in developing and emerging countries.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>Who we are</h2><ul><li>Founded in 1959 by leading Swiss companies and civil society.</li><li>Global Reach: active in 41 countries, managing 131 projects.</li><li>Team: ~1,200 staff, of which 95% are local employees.</li><li>Annual turnover: CHF 105 million, with approximately 20% private funding.</li></ul><p>We combine Swiss values such as quality, partnership, and efficiency with international experience and local roots.</p></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--50-50"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''7d77b823-2faa-4c21-9d27-99ae2db6513c'',''name'':''NPL_Sahaj-NAMDP_DSC00032.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''185860f3930f1ed014e39f3d94e89e44d3e212ec'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1600''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">What drives us</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">Our vision is an inclusive, sustainable economy where everyone has access to income, education, and opportunities. We align our work with the United Nations’ Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).<br><br>Our focus areas:<br><br><strong>Skills and employment</strong><br><strong>Enterprise development</strong><br><strong>Green transition</strong></p></div></article></div><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>How we work</h2><p>Swisscontact pursues a holistic approach, empowering local organisations and partners to achieve lasting impact. Through cooperation with international and local businesses, we foster fair working conditions and transparent communication. Our projects are managed with a standardised monitoring and results measurement system, and we continuously develop new learning methods, thereby strengthening our collective knowledge.</p></div></div></div><div class="container textBoxFullsize--element"><div class="textBoxFullsize--wrapper"><div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-11 col-lg-8"><h2>Our Partners</h2><p>We work closely with international donors, public institutions, companies, and foundations. Our projects are efficient, scalable, and sustainable, forming long-term development strategies.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''24a81912-87e7-40d6-919f-61e86584e61c'',''name'':''RWA_PROMOST_Swisscontact_Content_Gathering_for_TVETs___-_RV8_3274_%281%29.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''74326503c424cd66f972f6a3beb951d10f45be24'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1600''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">Would you like to get involved and support our work?</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">Find the right opportunity.</p><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us" class="variable-teaser__link"></a></div></article></div></div></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="