/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6ecd602a-f5e6-4796-887e-4072628cc869'',''name'':''Athgharey_Namuna_Krishi_Firm_SAHAJ-12.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''ba6502d118aaae18ce788958ad3863ed90629b9f'',''maxwidth'':''9265'',''originalwidth'':''9265'',''originalheight'':''4589''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.530491095521%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en/what-we-do"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">What we do</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Expertise</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Comprehensive development for sustainable prosperity</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">We strengthen individual skills to secure income, foster business competitiveness, and improve socio-economic systems. In doing so, we make lasting contributions to social and economic development.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h2>Skills and employment</h2></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="42325552-2427-4a6b-b69c-fbd18067f22e"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/initial-vocational-education-and-training"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6fb966d2-c4a9-4e4b-8729-b73d8873213f'',''name'':''Cover_Photo-1000x665.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''51e7edf2ff52a9abbc94e42ec47ea620662135fa'',''maxwidth'':''998'',''originalwidth'':''998'',''originalheight'':''665''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.633266533066%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Initial Vocational Education and Training: Professional skills for the world of work</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Vocational skills are essential for social inclusion and economic development. Yet many young people in developing countries lack access to vocational education. This is where Swisscontact steps in: we empower them to enter the labour market as skilled professionals or entrepreneurs. We promote education and training models where the &nbsp;private sector is in the driving seat to develop and offer demand based practical training pathways. This opens up new opportunities and helps reduce youth unemployment sustainably.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/initial-vocational-education-and-training" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="1c92373d-240c-4867-ac60-58f9ddbcb2d3"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/labour-market-insertion"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''cd8e6d1f-b32e-460b-b5d9-7a30681e7cfb'',''name'':''WA_Labour_Market_Insertion.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''cc9f84c78194ca1c4a04724c4315c39922358215'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Labour market insertion: creating opportunities for self-determined employment</div><div class="teaser__box--text">We build bridges between job seekers and a changing labour market. We support public services to engage non-governmental bodies and the private sector actors to establish effective labour market integration.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/labour-market-insertion" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="88232893-c4a8-4528-8688-e9d98e7eb292"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/reskilling-and-upskilling"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''ee4e16b5-42b1-424e-b7df-e43d27938e1d'',''name'':''NPL_Step-Up__SWISS_CONTACT_EV_REPAIRING_%2821%29.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''38fb501fad5e052da3717d40f9a206df8dbc8d8f'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Reskilling and upskilling: equipped for the future of work </div><div class="teaser__box--text">Technological innovation, demographic shifts, and climate change are reshaping the global labour market. For individuals and businesses alike, it is increasingly important to adapt to these changes with new skills. Swisscontact views upskilling and reskilling as key levers for a fair economy. We promote individual skills development, strengthening of employers and educational or training providers and other actors. This ensures long-term employability for workers and sustained efficiency for businesses.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/reskilling-and-upskilling" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h2>Enterprise development</h2></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="c8168c3b-53a2-4c3b-8345-1a6a5f7f7c52"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''69c7684c-1179-4181-baf6-b3f27c2ef039'',''name'':''NPL_Step-Up__SWISS_CONTACT_TV_REPAIR_CENTER_%2814%29.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''f31a2b07382c418d63002c021ea31544f6b28617'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Growth entrepreneurship: unleashing local innovation</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Local businesses create jobs, income, and opportunities for communities. We strengthen the structures, networks, and organisations that promote entrepreneurship. This fosters ecosystems where business ideas can flourish and markets open up. All the while, the social and environmental impact of entrepreneurial activity grows sustainably.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/growth-entrepreneurship" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="7d1f7902-a555-4201-8f5d-f8f833c2b432"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''8adf546f-5229-4671-b55b-2e08676ece67'',''name'':''8J8A0997.jpg'',''title'':''Sustainable Tourism Working Area'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''a19ab13b1ab5333e60211763ec5a788477fa2273'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Sustainable tourism: promoting local development, preserving culture, protecting the climate </div><div class="teaser__box--text">If designed inclusively and responsibly, tourism can be a powerful driver for development. Swisscontact works with local partners to develop tourism solutions that go beyond economic success: they preserve natural resources, respect cultural heritage, and empower local communities. This builds resilience of tourism ecosystems and creates long-term opportunities for both host communities and travellers.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/sustainable-tourism" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="707fef36-879b-41a6-baa3-6d0efe37c2a9"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''8dd51988-94e7-4eb9-b28d-b3930cb881fa'',''name'':''cocoa_trade_activities_%283%29.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''1e41049cfcf681b58df5cbe5ea202ae8678c344a'',''maxwidth'':''5184'',''originalwidth'':''5184'',''originalheight'':''3454''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.628086419753%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Trade: Promoting inclusive, sustainable and greener cross-border trade</div><div class="teaser__box--text">We are committed to fair, inclusive and sustainable economic structures and trade in developing countries. To promote cross-border trade and economic growth in developing countries, our projects strengthen production and value creation, reduce trade and structural barriers, and open up new market opportunities. We work with small and medium sized enterprises, governmental bodies, regulators and other critical organisations, such as payment providers, sector associations or certification bodies, to integrate developing countries better into global value chains.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/trade" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="69155312-aef9-4ac9-aeec-e51f8a255cf7"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''76a1b6f9-9d80-4b44-ae7b-c3f9c9f93bcd'',''name'':''BFA_Mara-Panga_2O2A7397_%281%29.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''c9ac14308c5f5a4c2eb8fca34dd65bf482911295'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Financial inclusion: Empowering people and businesses for sustainable growth</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Access to quality financial products and services is a catalyst for inclusive economic development. Yet, millions of individuals and countless small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) remain excluded from formal financial systems. Swisscontact bridges this gap – enabling people and businesses to save, invest, manage risk, and unlock their full potential. Our approach strengthens both individual financial health and the competitiveness of SMEs, fostering resilient communities and thriving local economies.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/financial-inclusion" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h2>Green transition</h2></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="72d4689b-6f2d-48dc-ab54-9b0e38e0e156"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''5cfa440b-ec26-44cd-a082-3dc9fa171da3'',''name'':''NPL_Sahaj-NAMDP_JBS_Sahaj_NAMDP-II_Swisscontact-2025-15.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''fbbebbb364f3e5120311571356a0f46f9aee9162'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Sustainable agriculture: pathways to resilient livelihoods, nutrition security and a healthy environment</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Agriculture is under pressure worldwide. Climate change, soil degradation, and market imbalances threaten the livelihoods of millions. A strong, inclusive agricultural sector is essential for stable incomes and food security. Swisscontact is committed to forward-looking solutions that help smallholder farms become more productive, climate-resilient, and environmentally friendly.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/sustainable-agriculture" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="49607627-a771-4822-8ce8-9852d136dbf9"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''dec5702d-da19-4fef-b442-30a60995f501'',''name'':''HO6A4002.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''288ffa4ad182086db917d50925e1fd323e513f3f'',''maxwidth'':''5760'',''originalwidth'':''5760'',''originalheight'':''3838''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.631944444444%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Green cities: creating greener and more inclusive urban spaces</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Cities are growing rapidly – along with their environmental and social challenges. Together with local partners, Swisscontact contributes to liveable, inclusive urban landscapes. Our projects promote green jobs and income through sustainable mobility, improved waste management, cleaner air, and circular economy practices – making cities more inclusive and resilient to climate change and rapid urbanisation.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/expertise/green-cities" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''18a44370-b3d8-4c8d-a12c-82754600d33d'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''47e3ecdea5c40aff4afc42d22ca97f1c6146a545'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1351''}" style="padding-bottom: 56.291666666667%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">Want to get involved and support us?</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">Find the right opportunity.</p><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us" class="variable-teaser__link"></a></div></article></div></div></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/imprint"><span class="item__footer--text">Imprint</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/privacy-statement"><span class="item__footer--text">Privacy statement</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/legal-notice"><span class="item__footer--text">Legal notice</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="javascript: UC_UI.showSecondLayer();"><span class="item__footer--text">Cookie settings</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="footer__content footer__centerContent col-lg-4"><div class="neos-contentcollection">
