av__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''ad8e4cd7-bdd7-4d51-b32c-b6af5686ee05'',''name'':''Tapasya_Sahaj-4.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''fef79b2630accd38bca7bf748cce2de6831ac530'',''maxwidth'':''9504'',''originalwidth'':''9504'',''originalheight'':''4707''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.526515151515%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en/what-we-do"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">What we do</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Impact</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Sustainable impact through systematics and data</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">Swisscontact consistently follows a data-driven approach to impact assessment, which constitutes an integral part of project management and quality assurance. Systematic monitoring enables results to be measured in a consistent manner, allowing us to gain insights, and consequently improve our projects effectively.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''12c971c9-230a-4e08-81a3-b08ee6654e30'',''name'':''RWA_PROMOST_Swisscontact_Content_Gathering_for_TVETs___-_RV8_0514.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''34ffbdd8be265e2b5a179399e40bd7b195d35243'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1199''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.958333333333%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">Measuring what works</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">The monitoring and impact system developed by Swisscontact is based on internationally recognized standards. Digitally supported tools and regular audits ensure the quality of data collection while providing continuously reliable results for internal management and external reporting.</p></div></article></div><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2 style="text-align:center;">Facts and figures (2021 – 2025)</h2></div></div></div><div class="container resultTeaserGroup threeColumn"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Skills development</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Over <strong>613,831 people</strong> completed training or vocational education programmes. <strong>178,456</strong> of them subsequently found a job or started their own business – generating additional income totaling <strong>CHF 124.6 million.</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Business promotion</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p><strong>7 million</strong> small businesses benefited from improved services. Of these, <strong>3.4 million</strong> reported additional income totalling <strong>CHF 650.5</strong> million, and <strong>214,413 jobs</strong> were newly created or secured.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Financial inclusion</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>More than <strong>1.3 million</strong> farmers, SMEs, and training participants gained access to financial services totalling <strong>CHF 1.3 billion.</strong> Women or women-led enterprises accounted for <strong>56%</strong> of these.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Environmental responsibility</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Swisscontact projects generated savings of over <strong>1.5 million tonnes </strong>of CO₂ and the reduction or recycling of <strong>56,117 tonnes</strong> of waste.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="resultTeaser position-relative text"><div class="resultTeaser__title--box" style="background-color:#eff0f2"><p class="titleColor grey">Gender Equality &amp; Social Inclusion</p></div><div class="resultTeaser__body--box"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="content__text"><p>Women represented <strong>47%</strong> of participants in training programmes, and roughly half of the total number of people who then found jobs or started their own businesses have been <strong>women </strong>(<strong>49%</strong>). In enterprise development projects, over <strong>39%</strong> of businesses were headed by women.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>Added value for all stakeholders</h2><ul><li>For projects: early identification of trends and bottlenecks enables flexible adjustments. Decisions are traceable and based on facts. This facilitates exchange of best practices within the organisation.</li><li>For Swisscontact: the globally standardised system strengthens internal learning, increases efficiency, and improves communication of results to donors and the public.</li><li>For Partners: reliable data builds trust and strengthens Swisscontact’s position as a professional, results-oriented implementing organisation. External audits confirm the quality of impact measurement.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--70-30"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''2105908e-d578-4e5c-b297-c3f7db0369fd'',''name'':''Sunrise_Dudh_Udhyog_Sahaj-10.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''ef6e843244a901189207215a5a03046f44a6ba57'',''maxwidth'':''9504'',''originalwidth'':''9504'',''originalheight'':''4750''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.978956228956%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">Would you like to get involved and support our work?</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text">Find the right opportunity.</p><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us" class="variable-teaser__link"></a></div></article></div><div class="container content__headline"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"></div></div></div></div></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/imprint"><span class="item__footer--text">Imprint</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/privacy-statement"><span class="item__footer--text">Privacy statement</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/legal-notice"><span class="item__footer--text">Legal notice</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="javascript: UC_UI.showSecondLayer();"><span class="item__footer--text">Cookie settings</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="footer__content footer__centerContent col-lg-4"><div class="neos-contentcollection">
