mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6159ff88-c18f-482f-8d27-9193ae08a971'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''531094119d262dbc60017c71d819ca76d8665e75'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li><li class="mainNav__item level1"><a href="/en/news"><span class="mainNav__text">News</span></a></li><li data-nezzo-mainnav-haschilds class="mainNav__item level1 sub"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a><div class="mainNav__level2--wrapper"><div class="mainNav__level2--content"><div><div class="mainNav__item--parent level2"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a></div><ul class="mainNav__level2" data-nezzo-mainnav-level="2"><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/mission-and-guiding-principles"><span class="mainNav__text">Mission and guiding principles</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><span class="mainNav__text">Sustainability strategy</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/code-of-conduct"><span class="mainNav__text">Code of conduct</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/foundation"><span class="mainNav__text">Foundation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/team"><span class="mainNav__text">Team</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''4acca297-facc-4012-8380-ea0c4509f926'',''name'':''DSC_0597.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''b1efe7d5d46fb0a9d7e6bc117ccf494be8466f77'',''maxwidth'':''6016'',''originalwidth'':''6016'',''originalheight'':''2980''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.534574468085%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en/what-we-do"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">What we do</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Working Principles</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>We shape effective development cooperation</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">Our working principles are the foundation of every project – from the first concept to impact assessment. They ensure quality, transparency, and efficiency in all that we do.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container"><article class="variable-teaser variable-teaser--50-50"><div class="variable-teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''8188afc9-a3a9-438e-be5a-32a1d23a05de'',''name'':''_A7R7305.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''38ada18aa0a89f8836f90b8b0ee71ad3233fe3d7'',''maxwidth'':''7805'',''originalwidth'':''7805'',''originalheight'':''5206''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.700832799488%"></div></div><div class="variable-teaser__content"><div class="variable-teaser__headline"><h2 class="variable-teaser__headline">Our working principles</h2></div><p class="variable-teaser__text"><strong>Private sector cooperation</strong><br>We cultivate and expand partnerships with local and international businesses to strengthen impact. We attach particular importance to fostering respectable work conditions with honest and fair communication.<br><br><strong>Systemic thinking</strong><br>Acting as trainers, facilitators, and enablers, we apply a systemic approach that empowers local organisations and partners to achieve sustainable impact at scale.<br><br><strong>Monitoring and Evaluation</strong><br>We manage our projects with an evidence-informed and adaptive management approach, using a standardized monitoring and results measurement system that allows for informed decision-making and timely corrective action.<br><br><strong>Learning culture</strong><br>We are constantly developing and embedding new learning methodologies. In close collaboration with our partners, we strive to increase our collective knowledge, competence, and performance to co-shape the future of international development work.</p></div></article></div><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h2>This is how we create trust and impact</h2><p>Our working principles enable us to implement projects efficiently and design them to scale, thereby anchoring them sustainably. Our principles ensure transparency vis-à-vis partners, donors, and the public; they are a key reason for the high quality and credibility of Swisscontact.</p></div></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h2>Learn more</h2></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="fa05243b-ba66-48a3-91ee-69d79d91cd78"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/what-we-do/impact"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''3e711d12-993c-44ff-8649-3a75bf9536a4'',''name'':''Tapasya_Sahaj-4.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''1439a36d3ca1cf0a21c77f911b138d5dd566023d'',''maxwidth'':''9504'',''originalwidth'':''9504'',''originalheight'':''6333''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.635101010101%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Our Approach to Impact</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Swisscontact consistently follows a data-driven approach to impact assessment, which constitutes an integral part of project management and quality assurance. Systematic monitoring enables results to be measured in a consistent manner, allowing us to gain insights, and consequently improve our projects effectively.</div></div><a href="/en/what-we-do/impact" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="c952c3fa-a514-4d17-b92f-49e1d95008e7"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''1ebb5cfc-353a-4d96-a8d6-a92effce8231'',''name'':''_MG_8013.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''fe4a9f47f5ddaea78a1f4600d7adbee596115235'',''maxwidth'':''5049'',''originalwidth'':''5049'',''originalheight'':''3368''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.706278470984%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Our Sustainability Strategy</div><div class="teaser__box--text">We combine economic progress, social justice, and environmental protection – in every project, partnership, and internal process. Our sustainability strategy demonstrates how we design development cooperation holistically and with a view to the future.</div></div><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="3f46a1be-79a2-48cd-9be8-daf8c7f1ff6a"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''eae4672f-5c2e-47bc-a94f-934385f4b233'',''name'':''Prodi_listrik_Morowali-2019__%28175%29_%281%29.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''b51715e672c2dcaf4618515a43282ec20ac877c8'',''maxwidth'':''5184'',''originalwidth'':''5184'',''originalheight'':''3454''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.628086419753%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">All Projects</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Our development work focuses on private sector-led, sustainable economic development with improved quality of life for all in developing and emerging countries.&nbsp;</span><span>A key focus is to strengthen</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>the skills of individuals and foster the competitiveness of companies.</span><span> </span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</div></div><a href="/en/projects" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div></main></div><footer class="d-print-none"><div class="footer__row footer__first-row"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="footer__content footer__leftContent col-lg-4"><div class="footerNav"><div class="footerNav__title"><h3>Legal</h3></div><div class="footerNav__items"><ul><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/imprint"><span class="item__footer--text">Imprint</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/privacy-statement"><span class="item__footer--text">Privacy statement</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="/en/footer/legal-notice"><span class="item__footer--text">Legal notice</span></a></li><li class="nav__item--footer"><a class="item__footer--link" href="javascript: UC_UI.showSecondLayer();"><span class="item__footer--text">Cookie settings</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="footer__content footer__centerContent col-lg-4"><div class="neos-contentcollection">
