ainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''379f3094-d7b0-4956-9fd3-f413c1a218f7'',''name'':''Albania_S4J_Tailor-training.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''42b781460ee76eecac524f749d1c4b4f434f9d15'',''maxwidth'':''2200'',''originalwidth'':''2200'',''originalheight'':''1090''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.545454545455%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en/where-we-work"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Where we work</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Albania</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content sideContent container"><div class="row"><div class="sideContent--left col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-7"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Albania</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">Albania is a middle-income country with high unemployment (14%-22%) and underemployment, particularly among youth (40%), and a large informal sector (&gt;30%) as key challenges. A functional democracy with improved public services and an inclusive, competitive market economy in support of the European integration are among the goals of international cooperation strategies for the country.</div></div></div></div><div class="country__sideContent col-12 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 col-xl-4"><div class="sideContent--box"><div class="sideContent--map"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-respectheight="true" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a470a5db-4c70-4b1f-87ea-f8e48e4c5d83'',''name'':''albania.png'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''a8cbaa80e6b9c6f086397e3f1e784ededa0498eb'',''maxwidth'':''664'',''originalwidth'':''664'',''originalheight'':''504''}"></div></div><div class="sideContent--headline">About Albania</div><div class="sideContent--infos"><h3>Country Facts</h3><ul><li>Area: in km<sup>2</sup>: 28,748</li><li>Population: 2,845,955</li><li>Capital: Tirana</li></ul><h3>Swisscontact in Albania</h3><ul><li>since 1994</li><li>6 running projects</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="backgroundContainer"><div class="container"><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h3>Projects</h3></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/projects?country=al" title="View all projects from Albania">View all projects from Albania</a></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="8e30d87f-86ec-4998-afcd-74ae4cf25c1d"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects/sippo" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''ea611efa-6146-4807-8e2a-16c217ee83ae'',''name'':''Sector_NI.png'',''title'':''SIPPO'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''14a3acb8aa8f6bb1406e9df47b7fd7ae01baa151'',''maxwidth'':''2619'',''originalwidth'':''2619'',''originalheight'':''1746''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2017 - 2029</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Albania, Bosnia & Herzegovina, Indonesia, Morocco, North Macedonia, Peru, Serbia, South Africa, Tunisia, Ukraine, Vietnam</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Trade, Initial vocational education and training, Growth entrepreneurship, Sustainable tourism</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Swiss Import Promotion Programme</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The Swiss Import Promotion Programme (SIPPO) is a well-established mandate of the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (SECO) within the framework of its economic development cooperation. The programme has been implemented by Swisscontact since 2017 and is now in phase 3.<br><br>The overall objective of SIPPO is to integrate developing and transition countries into world trade.&nbsp;In a facilitation role, SIPPO advises and supports so-called Business Support Organisations (BSOs) in 11 partner countries. Through innovative and targeted export promotion services, BSOs strengthen the export capabilities of companies intending to export and facilitate market access and exports to Switzerland, the EU, and regional markets.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/sippo" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="f037101e-375b-440c-a9b2-3b7083aaa4a0"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects/s4j" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''641456d9-0b85-41d1-b7ba-b1e84fa8ebf4'',''name'':''DSC03408.jpg'',''title'':''S4J Project Albania, Hamdi Bushati VET School Shkodra'',''alt'':''At “Hamdi Bushati” VET School in Shkodra, learning goes beyond the classroom. Through its partnership with the Skills for Jobs (S4J) project, the “Hamdi Bushati” VET School in Shkodra, learning goes beyond the classroom.'',''hash'':''bfa887cb3e66a8c0ea320607f4fdfc86ddd5f250'',''maxwidth'':''6000'',''originalwidth'':''6000'',''originalheight'':''3998''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.633333333333%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2015 - 2027</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Albania</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Initial vocational education and training, Sustainable tourism</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Skills for Jobs (S4J)</div><div class="teaser__box--text">‘Skills for Jobs’ (S4J) is a project mandated by the Swiss Agency for Development and Cooperation (SDC) and implemented by Swisscontact Albania. It is part of the Economic Development Domain of the Swiss Cooperation Strategy for Albania (2018-2021), with specific focus on promotion of employment opportunities and skills development.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/s4j" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="0d5b89b6-5476-4bdc-8e28-1a97bdf2a501"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects/swiss-entrepreneurship-programme" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''3be08550-dae1-4f2b-a3d3-b8789abbcffc'',''name'':''MKD_country_pic_%281%29.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''d447eb4e5eeab09b2f81963e43331ae1fadc3dc0'',''maxwidth'':''1351'',''originalwidth'':''1351'',''originalheight'':''901''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.691339748335%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2015 - 2027</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Albania, Bosnia & Herzegovina, Kosovo, North Macedonia, Peru, Serbia, Vietnam</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Growth entrepreneurship</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Swiss Entrepreneurship Program</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The heart of any entrepreneurial ecosystem is the community of entrepreneurs themselves. The Swiss Entrepreneurship Program (Swiss EP) has incorporated this belief and supports building local startup communities bottom up by working with ecosystem leaders and builders since 2015. We do this by working with selected startup support organizations...</div></div><a href="/en/projects/swiss-entrepreneurship-programme" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h3>News</h3></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/news?country=al" title="View all news from Albania">View all news from Albania</a></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 teaser--news" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="896a4483-1732-4d89-b83f-ce560a9cb14b"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news/how-small-businesses-are-shaping-eastern-europes-next-economy" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''88e5a40d-4458-4f5a-be52-5b6f35de6d8a'',''name'':''P1540782.jpg'',''title'':''UKR_Empower agriwomen_iana Skurat'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''0d38241d9ca5c1bb4b9a4847d5ee3b146cd9771c'',''maxwidth'':''4592'',''originalwidth'':''4592'',''originalheight'':''3061''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.659407665505%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Albania, Kosovo, North Macedonia, Georgia, Ukraine</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Sustainable agriculture, Growth entrepreneurship, Financial inclusion, Sustainable tourism, Trade</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--date">26.06.2026</div><div class="teaser__box--title">How small businesses are shaping Eastern Europe''s next economy</div><div class="teaser__box--text">For the Micro-, Small and Medium Enterprises Day, this year the United Nations has given it a theme that fits the moment well: empowering small businesses through innovation and sustainable industrial development. Micro, small and medium enterprises make up more than nine in ten businesses worldwide. They are where most people work, and where women, young people and those usually left out are most likely to find a way in.</div></div><a href="/en/news/how-small-businesses-are-shaping-eastern-europes-next-economy" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 teaser--news" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="2c8e488c-d316-43a3-9d14-8d1630b238f8"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news/gender-insights-to-improve-public-services-in-albania" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''87477d30-6bad-4c35-949c-d624ca17367b'',''name'':''2.png'',''title'':''afd_gesi assignment_durres 2'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''6bca23ccd8ee11a2c642e5f813b3e0ea2ffe5d94'',''maxwidth'':''1148'',''originalwidth'':''1148'',''originalheight'':''765''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.637630662021%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Albania</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--date">18.11.2025</div><div class="teaser__box--title">Gender insights to improve public services in Albania&nbsp;</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Swisscontact contributed to equitable infrastructure reform in Durrës through gender-focused institutional analysis in the water and sanitation sector.</div></div><a href="/en/news/gender-insights-to-improve-public-services-in-albania" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 teaser--news" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="47aa5278-8e84-441d-b72e-082fd29f1fef"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news/10-years-of-regional-impact-in-dual-vet" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''18ba4239-8bc6-4656-a14e-2a735185258e'',''name'':''DC_dVET_KOC9404.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''d21395134594731b97bbb0b5835735638626bb75'',''maxwidth'':''6000'',''originalwidth'':''6000'',''originalheight'':''3998''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.633333333333%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Albania, Kosovo</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Initial vocational education and training</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--date">06.11.2025</div><div class="teaser__box--title">10 Years of Regional Impact in Dual VET</div><div class="teaser__box--text">How Swisscontact is contributing to donor coordination and system reform in dual VET across the Western Balkans and Eastern Europe.</div></div><a href="/en/news/10-years-of-regional-impact-in-dual-vet" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><div class="multicolumn__twoCol"><div class="row twoCol--4and8"><div class="twoCol--left col-12 col-lg-4"><div class="content__director"><div class="director--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''5e57e689-f928-483f-b269-14fdd7df6c93'',''name'':''swisscontact-staff-002.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''a19ce3a1e755c05881850405ed9e97c91a36d781'',''maxwidth'':''9000'',''originalwidth'':''9000'',''originalheight'':''5997''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.633333333333%"></div></div><div class="director--text"><div class="director--role">Country Director Albania</div><div class="director--name">Argjentina Grazhdani</div></div></div></div><div class="2col--right col-12 col-lg-8"><div class="content__facts"><div class="facts--headline"><h3>Swisscontact in Albania</h3></div><div class="facts--text"><p>Swisscontact’s portfolio in Albania is the largest in the region. Through our projects, we contribute to equitable economic development, by building sustainable systems for vocational skills development and enterprise promotion.</p><p>Innovation, labour-market oriented training and private sector involvement are at the core of Swisscontact’s interventions in Albania. The goal is to provide more and better economic opportunities and perspectives to all, but especially to young women and men.</p><p>Swisscontact’s work in Albania is an essential part of Switzerland’s development strategy in the country.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container content__media d-print-none"><div class="row"><div class=" col-12"><div class="iframe__embedding--container d-print-none"><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/gNgXbv4G1Uo?iv_load_policy=3&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;autoplay=0&amp;rel=1&amp;controls=1&amp;hl=en" allowfullscreen allowtransparency allow="autoplay"></iframe></div></div></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/where-we-work/albania/videos-swisscontact-albania" title="More videos Swisscontact Albania">More videos Swisscontact Albania</a></div></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="d2884548-fb60-49af-bf84-f6e276a6ed91"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/where-we-work/albania/collaboration-opportunities"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''7db396c6-ee59-4ef2-8a09-415342e748a6'',''name'':''MRM_Manual_S4J_Title_image.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fdbe29446250736892af77fd5acdbb25d2f9ebb'',''maxwidth'':''843'',''originalwidth'':''843'',''originalheight'':''562''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Collaboration Opportunities</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Want to collaborate with Swisscontact? See available opportunities here. </div></div><a href="/en/where-we-work/albania/collaboration-opportunities" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="4d00fd88-5855-4ad6-936e-ff32263e2770"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/where-we-work/albania/jobs?country=al"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''41955cc9-22d3-40f5-8648-962eb34b99fe'',''name'':''5.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''e932f68ba9acf24b9867e9126e4042072192b8f2'',''maxwidth'':''6016'',''originalwidth'':''6016'',''originalheight'':''4008''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.622340425532%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Jobs</div><div class="teaser__box--text">See here available job opportunities from Swisscontact Albania</div></div><a href="/en/where-we-work/albania/jobs?country=al" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="5f805b19-e01d-4756-aa46-3271e47d87b1"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/about-us/team?country=al"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''1a1f4236-bae7-4eaa-b15e-6d983efdc0e6'',''name'':''7.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':''FoBBIZ'',''hash'':''a3d5e10b6c78832759ebb4110300b80a480f8407'',''maxwidth'':''6016'',''originalwidth'':''6016'',''originalheight'':''4008''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.622340425532%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Team</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The abilities and readiness for action of our employees are decisive for our projects’ ability to achieve sustainable impact, as well as our long-term success. As an attractive employer, Swisscontact invests in a positive management and work culture. This is defined by our fundamental understanding of development intended to serve not only our beneficiaries in project countries but our employees as well.</div></div><a href="/en/about-us/team?country=al" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="colored-contentbox"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container content__text"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><h3>Subscribe to the Swisscontact Eastern Europe Newsletter</h3></div></div></div><div class="container">
