ment"><span class="mainNav__text">Philanthropic Engagement</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us/public-development-cooperation"><span class="mainNav__text">Public Development Cooperation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us/support-swisscontact"><span class="mainNav__text">Support Swisscontact</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6159ff88-c18f-482f-8d27-9193ae08a971'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''531094119d262dbc60017c71d819ca76d8665e75'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li><li class="mainNav__item level1"><a href="/en/news"><span class="mainNav__text">News</span></a></li><li data-nezzo-mainnav-haschilds class="mainNav__item level1 sub"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a><div class="mainNav__level2--wrapper"><div class="mainNav__level2--content"><div><div class="mainNav__item--parent level2"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a></div><ul class="mainNav__level2" data-nezzo-mainnav-level="2"><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/mission-and-guiding-principles"><span class="mainNav__text">Mission and guiding principles</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><span class="mainNav__text">Sustainability strategy</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/code-of-conduct"><span class="mainNav__text">Code of conduct</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/foundation"><span class="mainNav__text">Foundation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/team"><span class="mainNav__text">Team</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''297cc445-99b0-4554-a01a-a2a6f5892ea1'',''name'':''bangladesh_header.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''1198ef65255f5c3efa24c29e92dc6db5f3bead63'',''maxwidth'':''1981'',''originalwidth'':''1981'',''originalheight'':''982''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.570923775871%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en/where-we-work"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Where we work</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Bangladesh</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content sideContent container"><div class="row"><div class="sideContent--left col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-7"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Bangladesh</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">Bangladesh</span><span>&nbsp;is one of the most populated countries in the world. This poses perpetual challenges in ensuring food security, education, decent jobs, and healthcare systems. However, the large population created an abundant supply of labour and a highly competitive labour market. For this reason, Bangladesh offers very low production costs and has become one of the most cost-efficient production hubs.</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</div></div></div></div><div class="country__sideContent col-12 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 col-xl-4"><div class="sideContent--box"><div class="sideContent--map"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-respectheight="true" data-ari-params="{''id'':''90fdf30b-7977-44df-bd93-c6835fcfbe57'',''name'':''bangladesh.png'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''81b3e83a59398a88580c68e2682a3eddecab5fec'',''maxwidth'':''663'',''originalwidth'':''663'',''originalheight'':''503''}"></div></div><div class="sideContent--headline">About Bangladesh</div><div class="sideContent--infos"><h3>Country Facts</h3><ul><li>Area in km<sup>2</sup>: 148,460</li><li>Population: 166.59 million</li><li>Capital: Dhaka</li></ul><h3>Swisscontact in Bangladesh</h3><ul><li>Since the 1970s</li><li>11 running projects</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="backgroundContainer"><div class="container"><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h3>Projects</h3></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/projects?country=bd" title="View all projects from Bangladesh">View all projects from Bangladesh</a></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="218ec630-4206-4fac-9a05-b82bf2903936"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''811c6ce0-7d2e-4237-a3db-15d66542a8b9'',''name'':''Shompritee_01.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''58845930f16ed89007c971cf2d93fb082b93fdf2'',''maxwidth'':''5400'',''originalwidth'':''5400'',''originalheight'':''3598''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.62962962963%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2025 - 2027</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Bangladesh</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Green cities</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Shompritee – Towards Locally Led Development for Climate Migrants</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Bangladesh ranks as the seventh most climate-vulnerable country, with coastal regions exposed to sea level rise, salinity intrusion, river erosion, and cyclones. These hazards have displaced millions, many of whom face inhumane conditions in urban areas, especially secondary cities.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/shompritee" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="f3251d98-28a2-4331-a660-a47e872c3838"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''ed46ff1a-602b-4ee4-bc5a-5ce48e5ca2d0'',''name'':''One_beautiful_picture.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''0be9b518bbd5ac797b4387ccdc0ec447aadf7bfb'',''maxwidth'':''1600'',''originalwidth'':''1600'',''originalheight'':''1067''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.6875%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2024 - 2027</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Bangladesh</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Green cities, Growth entrepreneurship</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">GO4IMPact – Improved Climate Resilient Public Service Delivery</div><div class="teaser__box--text">GO4IMPact aims at strengthening and improving equitable and climate resilient delivery of basic public services in Integrated Water Resource Management (IWRM) and Solid Waste Management (SWM). This will be achieved through a systemic, adaptive and facilitative approach to strengthen the capacities of relevant stakeholders including local government (Municipalities, Sub-district Councils and Rural Councils), with the central government and their line agencies, and also with private sector and Civil Society Groups.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/go4impact-improved-climate-resilient-public-service-delivery-through-local-government-institutions-in-water-and-solid-waste-management-sectors" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="ea5f2c7e-a05b-4557-b020-b987280a6c13"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects/technology-for-responsible-accountability-in-corporate-esg-trace" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''20ab6d29-2c88-4c23-a5d6-ab093d5cd91b'',''name'':''Effluent_Treatment_Plant_%28ETP%29_1.png'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''87413911450138758575febdf82ff9be26130124'',''maxwidth'':''5156'',''originalwidth'':''5156'',''originalheight'':''3438''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.679596586501%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2026 - 2027</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Bangladesh</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Growth entrepreneurship, Trade, Green cities</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Technology for Responsible Accountability in Corporate ESG (TRACE)</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The project aims to support the ready-made garment (RMG) industry in transitioning from fragmented, manual sustainability reporting to a digital, data-driven environmental, social and governance (ESG) management system. Through this centralised digital platform, factories, brands and service providers will be able to measure, manage and improve their environmental, social and governance performance, thereby enhancing their global competitiveness, compliance and climate resilience.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/technology-for-responsible-accountability-in-corporate-esg-trace" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="52407874-7e9d-4b42-930e-a7ec2190a722"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects/building-youth-employability-through-skills-byets" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''60313042-0c7d-4163-a877-9a788ca967bf'',''name'':''AP_08909.jpg'',''title'':''RMG worker in Bangladesh'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''23501d0b8702b94df1bfd6479af09f95d6bfc4c1'',''maxwidth'':''3504'',''originalwidth'':''3504'',''originalheight'':''2335''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.638127853881%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2022 - 2026</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Bangladesh</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Reskilling and upskilling, Labour market insertion</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Building Youth Employability through Skills (BYETS)</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The Building Youth Employability through Skills (BYETS) project aims to empower Bangladeshi young people by improving their technical, employability and entrepreneurial skills, and connecting them to income-generating opportunities, such as jobs and self-employment. BYETS collaborates with Training Service Providers (TSPs), the government, industry and employers to foster an environment conducive to employment opportunities for the target group.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/building-youth-employability-through-skills-byets" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="80177f6b-f93e-4812-befe-40ceb983be4d"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects/water-kiosks-social-enterprise-for-clean-and-affordable-drinking-water" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''54e070d1-08b6-413e-a22b-98d4b235b722'',''name'':''Bangladesh_H2O_school-based_welfare_model_kids_at_water_kiosk.png'',''title'':''students fill water bottles at water ATM in Baikari High School Bangladesh'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''0511bfc694071ec09947ca169e0ff29932a53ca1'',''maxwidth'':''2454'',''originalwidth'':''2454'',''originalheight'':''1634''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.585167074165%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2025 - 2028</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Bangladesh</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Growth entrepreneurship</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Water kiosks – Social enterprise for clean and affordable drinking water</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Despite clean drinking water being a fundamental human right, nearly 70 million people, about 40% of Bangladesh’s population, still lack reliable access. The challenge is most acute in rural areas and fast-growing (sub)urban regions, where polluted land and contaminated groundwater are common, and where public water supply networks remain out of reach. As a result, many families are forced to depend on informal water vendors, often paying high prices for water of uncertain quality.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/water-kiosks-social-enterprise-for-clean-and-affordable-drinking-water" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><div class="multicolumn__twoCol"><div class="row twoCol--4and8"><div class="twoCol--left col-12 col-lg-4"><div class="content__director"><div class="director--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''ebbe7bfb-8a65-43e5-8b44-a9a7eb2cf77c'',''name'':''Helal_Hussain_SC_Website.jpg'',''title'':''Helal Hussain_Country Director Bangladesh'',''alt'':''Helal Hussain_Country Director Bangladesh'',''hash'':''d334b9caef1ec70e77f111c27c875e6e636363dd'',''maxwidth'':''3266'',''originalwidth'':''3266'',''originalheight'':''2178''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.687078995713%"></div></div><div class="director--text"><div class="director--role">Country Director</div><div class="director--name">Helal Hussain</div></div></div></div><div class="2col--right col-12 col-lg-8"><div class="content__facts"><div class="facts--headline"><h3>Swisscontact in Bangladesh</h3></div><div class="facts--text"><p>We at Swisscontact Bangladesh would like to extend our heartfelt gratitude to our valued partners and collaborators. Through our partnership with the government, development partners, private sector, NGOs and communities, we have implemented projects across key sectors including agriculture, ready-made garments, light engineering, health, water and sanitation, financial inclusion, and microinsurance.</p><p>Our work has empowered farmers, women, and youth, fostering entrepreneurship, decent work, and climate resilience. These achievements reflect our partners’ unwavering commitment. Moving forward, we aim to deepen our collaborations to accelerate growth and tackle emerging challenges.&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you for being part of this remarkable journey! We look forward to even stronger alliances with you to address Bangladesh’s evolving development needs, and as always, build a future that is inclusive and leaves no one behind.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h2>News and Stories</h2></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="https://www.swisscontact.online/en/news?country=bd" title="view all news, articles and stories from Bangladesh">view all news, articles and stories from Bangladesh</a></div><div class="teaserproxy__3col col-12 col-md-4" data-internezzo-teaser--groupedproxy data-internezzo-teaser--proxyajaxuri="/en?ajaxDestination%5Bidentifier%5D=teaserProxyResolver&amp;ajaxDestination%5BteaserNodeIdentifier%5D=62a2436a-ee11-4954-bc28-fd0adbce311a&amp;ajaxDestination%5Bindex%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5BisLatest%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5Blanguage%5D="><div class="loader"><div class="loader__icon icon--top"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--center"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--bottom"></div></div></div><div class="teaserproxy__3col col-12 col-md-4" data-internezzo-teaser--groupedproxy data-internezzo-teaser--proxyajaxuri="/en?ajaxDestination%5Bidentifier%5D=teaserProxyResolver&amp;ajaxDestination%5BteaserNodeIdentifier%5D=62a2436a-ee11-4954-bc28-fd0adbce311a&amp;ajaxDestination%5Bindex%5D=1&amp;ajaxDestination%5BisLatest%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5Blanguage%5D="><div class="loader"><div class="loader__icon icon--top"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--center"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--bottom"></div></div></div><div class="teaserproxy__3col col-12 col-md-4" data-internezzo-teaser--groupedproxy data-internezzo-teaser--proxyajaxuri="/en?ajaxDestination%5Bidentifier%5D=teaserProxyResolver&amp;ajaxDestination%5BteaserNodeIdentifier%5D=62a2436a-ee11-4954-bc28-fd0adbce311a&amp;ajaxDestination%5Bindex%5D=2&amp;ajaxDestination%5BisLatest%5D=0&amp;ajaxDestination%5Blanguage%5D="><div class="loader"><div class="loader__icon icon--top"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--center"></div><div class="loader__icon icon--bottom"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="61bdcf34-c030-476d-b788-063fd7ec82c8"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive