></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us/public-development-cooperation"><span class="mainNav__text">Public Development Cooperation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/get-involved-with-us/support-swisscontact"><span class="mainNav__text">Support Swisscontact</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''6159ff88-c18f-482f-8d27-9193ae08a971'',''name'':''IND_SS4C_DSCF8110.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''531094119d262dbc60017c71d819ca76d8665e75'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li><li class="mainNav__item level1"><a href="/en/news"><span class="mainNav__text">News</span></a></li><li data-nezzo-mainnav-haschilds class="mainNav__item level1 sub"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a><div class="mainNav__level2--wrapper"><div class="mainNav__level2--content"><div><div class="mainNav__item--parent level2"><a href="/en/about-us"><span class="mainNav__text">About us</span></a></div><ul class="mainNav__level2" data-nezzo-mainnav-level="2"><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/mission-and-guiding-principles"><span class="mainNav__text">Mission and guiding principles</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/sustainability-strategy"><span class="mainNav__text">Sustainability strategy</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/code-of-conduct"><span class="mainNav__text">Code of conduct</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/foundation"><span class="mainNav__text">Foundation</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/team"><span class="mainNav__text">Team</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/history"><span class="mainNav__text">History</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/annual-reports"><span class="mainNav__text">Annual reports</span></a></li><li class="mainNav__item level2"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs"><span class="mainNav__text">Jobs</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="mainNav__level2--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a486b7d2-045a-4a77-baa1-704e4851e68c'',''name'':''KHM_SDP_Back_Cover_1.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''3fbb2100ff065e1f1d307db2c88a6e39ceba85cc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1189''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.541666666667%"></div></div><button class="mainNav__level2--close"><span class="mainNav__level2--close-icon"></span><span class="sr-only">Close Menü</span></button></div></div></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="header__wrapper--logo"><div class="header--logo"><a href="/en" title="Homepage"><img alt="Homepage" src="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Static/Packages/Internezzo.Neos/Images/logo_swisscontact.svg?bust=435ac641" /></a></div></div></div></header><div class="page"><div class="body--overlay d-print-none" data-internezzo-body--overlay></div><div class="header__image content--header__image"><div class="header__image--inner"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''878b834e-76eb-47ea-8dea-570309b5687a'',''name'':''B%C3%A9nin_FoRCE_CFL.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''e359d7d6afcca5d425231ea34235b439756deae2'',''maxwidth'':''1867'',''originalwidth'':''1867'',''originalheight'':''925''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.544724156401%"></div></div></div><div class="nav__breadcrumb"><ol><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en/where-we-work"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Where we work</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Bénin</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content sideContent container"><div class="row"><div class="sideContent--left col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-7"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Bénin</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">The primary thrust of Benin’s economic policy is to achieve a sufficient level of economic growth to be able to decrease poverty significantly. This includes broader economic diversification through the development of multiple structured value chains and incorporating agro-industrial processing in application of the principle of supply chain value addition. It also involves more effective management of public spending and more equitable geographic distribution of resources.</span><span>&nbsp;</div></div></div></div><div class="country__sideContent col-12 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 col-xl-4"><div class="sideContent--box"><div class="sideContent--map"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-respectheight="true" data-ari-params="{''id'':''c2ab6983-6efd-45a8-96a3-fc1766304af7'',''name'':''benin.png'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''050ab28a49603b75440e5a6015e019e648bb9b10'',''maxwidth'':''663'',''originalwidth'':''663'',''originalheight'':''503''}"></div></div><div class="sideContent--headline">BéNIN</div><div class="sideContent--infos"><h3><strong>Figures</strong></h3><ul><li>Area: 122.622 km2</li><li>Population: 11,53 million</li><li>Capital:&nbsp;Porto-Novo</li></ul><h3><strong>Swisscontact in Bénin</strong></h3><ul><li>since 2002</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="backgroundContainer"><div class="container"><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h3>Projects</h3></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/projects?country=bj" title="View all projects from Benin">View all projects from Benin</a></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="d4f5fa7c-5725-4b34-802b-6f2063e02e5a"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''48ec53d2-1e2e-452a-8985-e49e8046c28c'',''name'':''benininclusive.png'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''c7d379eee907be39000162a88c4af8404ff72038'',''maxwidth'':''2027'',''originalwidth'':''2027'',''originalheight'':''1350''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.60088801184%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2025 - 2026</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Sustainable agriculture, Growth entrepreneurship</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Beninclusive – Inclusion of small producers in climate-resilient markets </div><div class="teaser__box--text">The project supports two sectors:  fish farming and citrus fruit production. It aims to adapt both agricultural value chains to the challenges of climate change. Innovative and agroecological alternatives to traditional fish feed or fertilisers are provided to enable a systemic transition to climate-resilient and sustainable practices.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/beninclusive" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="533c1150-4ea1-4c0b-bc30-be3c155b7aa4"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''56c40ea9-ac6b-42db-8a3a-3e9754d00020'',''name'':''SEC_Bussink_Medicine_Nepal_2010.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''1e3aca9d8a1e42bb4bcab051e2b99e7fdc9d0df5'',''maxwidth'':''1943'',''originalwidth'':''1943'',''originalheight'':''1296''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.700977869274%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin, Bolivia, Cambodia, Kosovo, Nepal, Peru</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Growth entrepreneurship</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Senior Expert Contact</div><div class="teaser__box--text"> Promoting entrepreneurship through expertise - Imparting technical skills through volunteer work Through their services, Senior Expert Contact (SEC) experts provide hands-on, direct support to companies and institutions in their efforts to grow. <br />
Website</div></div><a href="/en/projects/sec" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__2col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row"><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="e41c1d17-b73b-4171-b39b-063cb5fae8e7"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''55a1f45c-96a8-49bc-a18d-1c3141df13c5'',''name'':''Benin_WAF_FORCE.jpeg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''e3e24959e9a995da604247a5214e7562e26bbad5'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2023 - 2026</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Initial vocational education and training, Reskilling and upskilling, Labour market insertion</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Vocational education for the labour market&nbsp;</span><span>(FORCE)</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The programme is helping to create a more efficient and attractive vocational education system with apprenticeship training, which in turn engenders inclusive socio-economic development in Benin.</span><span><br>Project activities support the implementation of a national strategy for technical training and vocational education. This includes easier access to training courses in promising future professions for young people, strengthening the national education system, and supporting various reforms to improve governance in vocational education.</div></div><a href="/en/projects/force" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__2col col-12 col-lg-6 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="d2e76a1f-a17f-4cb0-a161-bf46116f4074"><div class="teaser__image teaser__image--2col"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''c13f6c64-5af2-4236-8797-6d7ea6092c26'',''name'':''kpongou_femmes_champ.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''bc679e6ad2b5f8a4b35a55d8de328876203c5327'',''maxwidth'':''5472'',''originalwidth'':''5472'',''originalheight'':''3646''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.630116959064%"></div></div><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2020 - 2024</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Growth entrepreneurship</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Rural Economic Development Support Programme PASDER</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The four departments in the northern part of the country (Alibori, Borgou, Atacora and Donga) cover almost three quarters of the country''s surface area and are home to just over a third (33.9%) of the population. According to the Human Development Index (HDI) of 0.485, Benin will rank 167th out of 187 countries in 2016. Poverty has increased at...</div></div><a href="/en/projects/rural-economic-development-support-programme-pasder" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><div class="teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaserGroup__headline col-12"><h3>News</h3></div><div class="teaserGroup__link col-12"><a href="/en/news?country=bj" title="View all news from Benin">View all news from Benin</a></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 teaser--news" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="4a8617e4-def4-48fd-8768-e6b3dc6717a4"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news/what-if-weve-been-missing-half-the-solution-men-as-allies-in-womens-empowerment" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''82f718b2-636e-4fe4-a630-f553ceaf8566'',''name'':''Title_image.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''6beb061787ad721520cb9754c1590410eeccdb8a'',''maxwidth'':''4032'',''originalwidth'':''4032'',''originalheight'':''2688''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>DR Congo, Niger, Benin</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--date">06.03.2026</div><div class="teaser__box--title">What if we’ve been missing half the solution? Men as allies in women’s empowerment</div><div class="teaser__box--text">These are facts we all know: Across different contexts, women and girls are less likely to enrol in Vocational Education and Training (VET). Even when they do, social norms often limit their access to the full range of training and career choices. Consequently, they tend to remain in professions that are less valued and less remunerated, with limited prospects for economic advancement. Once they finish VET trainings, many women and girls in countries of developing and emerging economies do not enter the world of work due to social expectations that assign them unpaid care responsibilities and restrict their mobility.&nbsp;</div></div><a href="/en/news/what-if-weve-been-missing-half-the-solution-men-as-allies-in-womens-empowerment" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 teaser--news" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="3a92b695-86e8-49c2-9311-1dd70aa2bccc"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news/local-fish-feed-production-promising-advances-for-sustainable-aquaculture-in-benin" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''cd92e3d6-f5d5-4425-ad33-40c339a1edae'',''name'':''B%C3%A9nin_B%C3%A9ninclusif_PPP.3jpg.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''aa343121cf4459eb0dbe9e3c2d9ebb22f6b9850d'',''maxwidth'':''1102'',''originalwidth'':''1102'',''originalheight'':''734''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.606170598911%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Sustainable agriculture</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--date">17.12.2024</div><div class="teaser__box--title">Local fish feed production – promising advances for sustainable aquaculture in Benin</div><div class="teaser__box--text"><span>The Challenge: A Limiting Dependence on Imported Feed<br>&nbsp;</span><span>Aquaculture in Benin has been experiencing rapid growth. However, a major obstacle has hindered its potential: dependence on imported fish feed. Expensive, insufficient, and sometimes of inconsistent quality, these products have constrained fish farmers'' margins and their ability to compete in the local market. This raised a crucial question: how can locally-produced, high-quality, affordable, and eco-friendly feed ensure the sector''s sustainability?</span></div></div><a href="/en/news/local-fish-feed-production-promising-advances-for-sustainable-aquaculture-in-benin" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 teaser--news" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="35171163-f83f-4687-a554-2542e2def2bb"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news/when-training-meets-business-the-fo-rce-program-is-transforming-benin" title="Learn more"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''c3d73769-3baf-4fea-b137-f6e7567516f4'',''name'':''B%C3%A9nin_FoRCE_R%C3%A9seau_entreprise_3.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''c7879225846861fc4925e76c49d959146b4aeddc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Initial vocational education and training</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--date">21.10.2024</div><div class="teaser__box--title">When Training Meets Business: The FoRCE Program is Transforming Benin</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Since 2022, the FoRCE program has been supporting vocational training reforms in Benin by building strong bridges between training centers and local businesses. In response to the shortage of skilled labor in key sectors such as construction and automotive and motorcycle mechanics, this program, funded by the Swiss Cooperation, aims to address market needs while improving youth employability. Discover how this initiative strengthens collaboration between artisans, trainers, and entrepreneurs to create a more promising professional future in Benin.</div></div><a href="/en/news/when-training-meets-business-the-fo-rce-program-is-transforming-benin" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><div class="multicolumn__twoCol"><div class="row twoCol--4and8"><div class="twoCol--left col-12 col-lg-4"><div class="content__director"><div class="director--image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''d4a9f3f9-9b21-450c-a6b8-2afe21960b91'',''name'':''emmanuel-bossennec.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''aed3a6931ad4ed92cd5de24b53586e22af863ddc'',''maxwidth'':''2400'',''originalwidth'':''2400'',''originalheight'':''1599''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></div><div class="director--text"><div class="director--role">Directeur Bénin</div><div class="director--name">Emmanuel Bossennec</div></div></div></div><div class="2col--right col-12 col-lg-8"><div class="content__facts"><div class="facts--headline"><h3>Our approach</h3></div><div class="facts--text"><p>To push economic development and fight poverty we are implementing programmes in two specific domains: skills development and enterprise development.&nbsp;</p><p>We apply principles of subsidiarity, an organizing principle that matters ought to be handled by the least centralized and most local competent authority, in addition to sustainability and facilitation of autonomy in project implementation. We are always searching to anchor our interventions in close alignment with the public and private sector actors whom we support and in whom we believe. Our support, along with the help offered by our various implementation partners, must align with the socio-cultural logic and realities of local Beninese communities. This support focuses on the following:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>SME development&nbsp;</li><li>Development of vocational education and training&nbsp;</li><li>Certification and accreditation of vocational training&nbsp;</li><li>Organising the supply and demand of training&nbsp;</li><li>Labour market integration and youth employment&nbsp;</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container content__button"><div class="d-print-none btn"><p class="btn--linked"><a href="https://www.swisscontact.online/fr/pays/benin">Additional news and content on the&nbsp;french version of this page</span><span>&nbsp;</a></p></div></div><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="0249b5ac-2d82-4538-9856-db93e0a78c9d"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/where-we-work/benin/notre-approche"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''5d75bd97-8a4e-42f7-8492-27a84e72191a'',''name'':''_MG_2364.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''80261d243d1639741df4a16148a928226bdbe485'',''maxwidth'':''5472'',''originalwidth'':''5472'',''originalheight'':''3646''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.630116959064%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Notre approche</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Swisscontact est présente au Bénin depuis 2002. Pour favoriser le développement économique et la lutte contre la pauvreté, nous exécutons des programmes dans deux domaines à savoir : le développement des compétences et la promotion des entreprises.&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</div></div><a href="/en/where-we-work/benin/notre-approche" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="68f41ad9-d588-46d4-a926-ef368ab0546f"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/where-we-work/benin/domaines-dinterventions"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''7ceab4e7-a2cd-43c9-8b7d-430985051d47'',''name'':''_DSC2685.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''59c89ac57d784a325a6cf1733d02834bcd4fa053'',''maxwidth'':''5472'',''originalwidth'':''5472'',''originalheight'':''3646''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.630116959064%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Domaines d''interventions</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Swisscontact Bénin a démarré ses activités en 2002. Elle s''est donnée pour ambition d’accompagner les acteurs publics et privés pour favoriser l’employabilité, l’amélioration des revenus et l’augmentation de la productivité dans le secteur de l''artisanat et de l''agriculture.</div></div><a href="/en/where-we-work/benin/domaines-dinterventions" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 " data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="69436fb1-f7ca-473c-a0a1-8241f2b9b637"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/about-us/jobs?country=bj"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''46ad900f-54fa-47fb-81f5-c0bc1c1e0b64'',''name'':''Niger_FOPROR_Woman-writing-school_2019.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''5f9fd197818c2cf2dc4cd94ed57433a837a38758'',''maxwidth'':''5472'',''originalwidth'':''5472'',''originalheight'':''3646''}" style="padding-bottom: 66.630116959064%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Achieving impact worldwide</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The objective of Swisscontact’s work is to open up pathways out of poverty for people in developing countries through broad-based economic development projects.<br />
<br />
Motivated and productive employees with initiative constitute the most important success factor in all areas of our work. We count on motivated individuals who are looking to the future, impact- and team-oriented, and want to work in international development cooperation.<br />
</div></div><a href="/en/about-us/jobs?country=bj" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__fullsize" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="3b257475-cc07-438b-84f6-b38f8b158c2f"><div class="teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''a37e1915-0b86-47f7-b42d-cc0befedfecf'',''name'':''Formatrices_des_CFPA.jpg'',''title'':''PAFP_Benin_Formatrices des CFPA'',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''e1bba5f4c2042d2a9369e6819d0810e6e497a9fa'',''maxwidth'':''3872'',''originalwidth'':''3872'',''originalheight'':''1937''}" style="padding-bottom: 50.025826446281%"></div></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="container"><div class="teaser__box--wrapper col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 col-xl-5 offset-xl-0 col-xxl-4"><div class="teaser__box--content"><div class="teaser__box--tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-duration"><span>2017 - 2019</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-country"><span>Benin</span></div></div><div class="teaser__tagGroup"><div class="teaser__tagGroup--tag tags-workingArea"><span>Initial vocational education and training</span></div></div></div><div class="teaser__box--title">Un engagement de longue date en faveur de l’amélioration de la qualité de la Formation Professionnelle au Bénin</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Arrivés à terme fin 2019, après respectivement plus de quatre et six années de fonctionnement, il<br>ne fait nul doute que les projets AFPIJE et PAFPA ont apporté, de par les nombreuses bonnes pratiques et innovations, une réelle valeur ajoutée au système de la formation professionnelle au Bénin en termes de stratégies, afin d’en améliorer sa pertinence, sa qualité et sa performance.</div></div><div class="teaser__box--link"><a href="/en/projects/pafp-afpije" class="teaser--link" title="Learn more"><span class="teaser--link-text">Learn more</span></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container content__assetlist"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="assetlist__title"></div><div class="assetlist__list"><div class="asset__element"><a target="_blank" class="asset__element--link" href="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Persistent/b/0/0/3/b003ea15d43d4ae7844faf2fbccc50ed5fe7a9a3/Rapport_annuel_Afrique_de_l_Ouest_et_du_Nord_2019_web.pdf" title="Rapport annuel Afrique de l''Ouest et du Nord 2019"><div class="asset__element--title asset--file">Rapport annuel Afrique de l''Ouest et du Nord 2019</div></a><div class="asset__element--infos"><span class="asset__element--size">3 MB</span></div></div><div class="asset__element"><a target="_blank" class="asset__element--link" href="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Persistent/3/1/7/b/317b0a0fddc881ddf6a4482cfc390e46d5792103/Swisscontact_Afrika_West_2019_2_no_marks.pdf" title="Brochure de l''Afrique de l''ouest"><div class="asset__element--title asset--file">Brochure de l''Afrique de l''ouest</div></a><div class="asset__element--infos"><span class="asset__element--size">2 MB</span></div></div><div class="asset__element"><a target="_blank" class="asset__element--link" href="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Persistent/b/3/8/a/b38a49ed220400222386dd342c4110197704404c/Brochure_FP_Benin.pdf" title="Brochure sur la Formation professionnelle"><div class="asset__element--title asset--file">Brochure sur la Formation professionnelle</div></a><div class="asset__element--infos"><span class="asset__element--size">4 MB</span></div></div><div class="asset__element"><a target="_blank" class="asset__element--link" href="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Persistent/2/9/9/8/29986c5b939bc9bde46df146a76b990fad5c19e6/Afpije_und_Pafpa.pdf" title="Capitalisation sur les projets des projets AFPIJE et PAFPA"><div class="asset__element--title asset--file">Capitalisation sur les projets des projets AFPIJE et PAFPA</div></a><div class="asset__element--infos"><span class="asset__element--size">16 MB</span></div></div><div class="asset__element"><a target="_blank" class="asset__element--link" href="https://www.swisscontact.online/_Resources/Persistent/0/f/2/6/0f26d95b0bcbde698d8780b18f7ab1e3427506d9/Andragogie_Benin_low.pdf" title="L''andragogie dans la formation par apprentissage de type dual"><div class="asset__element--title asset--file">L''andragogie dans la formation par apprentissage de type dual</div></a><div class="asset__element--infos"><span class="asset__element--size">3 MB</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__fullsize" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="5f805b19-e01d-4756-aa46-3271e47d87b1"><div class="teaser__image"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{''id'':''c1070665-0cf5-461f-8926-7996f591642c'',''name'':''Benin_PAFPA_Woman-writing_2019.jpg'',''title'':'''',''alt'':'''',''hash'':''ba77ca4e58a61e6adda29a5057396e746c251b05'',''maxwidth'':''5472'',''originalwidth'':''5472'',''originalheight'':''2735''}" style="padding-bottom: 49.981725146199%"></div></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="container"><div class="teaser__box--wrapper col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 col-xl-5 offset-xl-0 col-xxl-4"><div class="teaser__box--content"><div class="teaser__box--title">Team</div><div class="teaser__box--text">The abilities and readiness for action of our employees are decisive for our projects’ ability to achieve sustainable impact, as well as our long-term success. As an attractive employer, Swisscontact invests in a positive management and work culture. This is defined by our fundamental understanding of development intended to serve not only our beneficiaries in project countries but our employees as well.</div></div><div class="teaser__box--link"><a href="/en/about-us/team?country=bj" class="teaser--link" title="Learn more"><span class="teaser--link-text">Learn more</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="contain